@DATABASE "Herbert's Dummy Run"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - H - Herbert's Dummy Run"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - H
                   ====================================

                            Herbert's Dummy Run
                            ===================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(36739,255)"}               36739,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Note that this POKE makes a bit of a mess
                         of the lives and score counters, but it
                         still works OK..
                                          Rastan
@endnode
